u.s. trade deficit 38.37 billion dlr in 4th qtr the u.s. merchandi trade deficit on a balanc of payment basi wa a record 38.37 billion dlr in the octob to decemb fourth quarter , the commerc depart said . the record trade shortfal came after a revi 37.15 billion dlr third quarter deficit . the depart previou report the third quarter deficit wa 37.67 billion dlr . for the full year 1986 , the merchandi trade deficit wa a record 147.7 billion dlr , up from 124.4 billion dlr in 1985 , the depart said . dure the final quarter last year import rose 2.78 billion dlr or three pct to 95.7 billion dlr , while export rose 1.56 billion dlr or three pct to 57.33 billion dlr . the trade report on a balanc of payment basi exclud such factor as militari sale and the cost of ship and insur . the commerc depart said non-petroleum import in the quarter were up 2.7 billion dlr or three pct to 87.7 billion dlr , with the largest increa in consum good , which rose 1.2 billion dlr , and in non-monetari gold and passeng car from canada , up 900 mln dlr each . lumber import from canada fell 300 mln dlr or 33 pct becau of a 15 pct duti on import from canada , the depart said . passeng car import fell 600 mln dlr becau of an 18 pct decrea in the number of south korean-mad import car and a nine pct decrea from japan . on the export side , agricultur export rose 600 mln dlr or nine pct to 7.1 billion dlr , primarili becau of a 104 pct or 600 mln dlr increa in soybean export . soybean shipment to western europ rose sharpli becau suppli from brazil , a tradit major export , were limit by drought . commerc said the u.s. trade deficit with latin america rose 900 mln dlr to 2.6 billion dlr , with japan increa 700 mln dlr to 14.8 billion dlr and with western europ rose 200 mln to 7.2 billion dlr in the quarter . the deficit with newli industri far east countri , includ hong kong , south korea , singapor and taiwan , fell 500 mln dlr to eight billion dlr and with canada the deficit decrea 200 mln dlr to 3.3 billion dlr in the quarter . in the full year 1986 , import rose 30.6 billion dlr or nine pct to 369.5 billion dlr . export increa by onli 7.3 billion dlr or three pct to 221.8 billion dlr . commerc said petroleum import dure 1986 fell 16.6 billion dlr or 33 pct to 33.9 billion dlr becau of lower price . the averag price per barrel decrea to 14.72 dlr from 26.41 dlr . agricultur export fell by 2.6 billion dlr or nine pct to 26.9 billion dure the year . the averag price of rice fell 27 pct , cotton wa down 22 pct , corn 18 pct , wheat 16 pct and soybean nine pct . the trade deficit with japan for all of 1986 rose 11.1 billion dlr to 54.6 billion dlr and with western europ increa 7.2 billion dlr to 28.6 billion dlr .